Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.51,0:00:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.47,0:00:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.39,0:00:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.24,0:00:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.76,0:00:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.97,0:00:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.62,0:00:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.52,0:00:35.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.11,0:00:40.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.95,0:00:47.06,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:52.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.77,0:00:58.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever, I take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.46,0:01:06.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it’s not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.72,0:01:16.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.43,0:01:21.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard someone else’s biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.55,0:01:25.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn’t there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.36,0:01:30.81,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.83,0:01:36.31,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.33,0:01:42.57,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.59,0:01:48.25,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.27,0:01:52.81,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.83,0:01:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.02,0:01:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.77,0:02:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.31,0:02:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.29,0:02:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.37,0:02:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.34,0:02:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.46,0:02:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.95,0:02:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demon Aura... Nine-Sword Style...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.23,0:02:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Asura!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.90,0:02:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sky Slicer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.79,0:02:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hardships are fine by me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.17,0:03:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I choose to walk the path of Asura!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.48,0:03:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asura... Silver Mist!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second Gear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.85,0:03:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jet Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.46,0:03:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shave!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.25,0:03:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finger Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.20,0:03:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.70,0:03:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Iron Body!\N--...Jet Bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.19,0:03:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.88,0:03:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please save Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.13,0:03:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just super leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.28,0:03:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bitch! You still don't get it?!\NI said this is useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.14,0:03:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do I have to tell you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.25,0:03:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no hope left for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:04:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.74,0:04:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll all come to rescue me for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.71,0:04:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Spandam Frightened!\NThe Hero on the Tower of Law"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.74,0:04:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, look at that!\NI've never seen this before!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.15,0:04:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I've never even heard\Nanyone talking about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.25,0:04:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To see that the Gates of Justice\Nhave completely opened!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so that the battleships from\NHeadquarters can come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.58,0:05:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's for the Buster Call's cannon attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Granny Kokoro surely said
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.38,0:05:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that those doors never\Nopen all the way, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.75,0:05:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this air of intimidation?\NWhat on earth is Buster Call?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.77,0:05:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats picked a fight with the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.15,0:05:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they really are going to blow them\Naway along with the entire island!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.24,0:05:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.02,0:05:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't die, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.21,0:05:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.48,0:05:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.18,0:05:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.56,0:05:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I entrusted Franky with saving Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.98,0:05:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was careless of me. I never\Nexpected him to be this powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.57,0:06:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that you're really out of breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.40,0:06:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it because of that steam?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.01,0:06:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Defeating you is all that matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.36,0:06:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... You're tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.96,0:06:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd better make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go yet, Nico Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.34,0:06:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look so stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.91,0:06:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because of your pointless\Nresistance, you dumb woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.14,0:06:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said, stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.41,0:06:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, the gate is right there, and yet\Nyou're causing me all sorts of trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.49,0:06:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guards! Go outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.24,0:07:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guards at the Gates of Justice,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.25,0:07:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and marines on the escort ship\Nsent by Navy Headquarters...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.50,0:07:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cipher Pol's Chief Spandam is currently\Ntaking a criminal of utmost importance
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,across the bridge from the Tower of Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.45,0:07:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All line up and salute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.90,0:07:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.37,0:07:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that. They're all ready to set sail now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.26,0:07:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no longer anything standing in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.61,0:07:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, Nico Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.45,0:07:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you in on a little secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.81,0:07:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before we crossed the bridge,\NI turned on the landmine
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,set on the upper part of the\Nstairs that we just ascended.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.78,0:08:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If, by any chance, someone\Ntries to make their way here,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.31,0:08:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they and the stairs will both go boom!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think? Isn't that interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.34,0:08:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, well, don't worry about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.62,0:08:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since no one's gonna make\Nit to those stairs anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.11,0:08:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't go through... the gate...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.06,0:08:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.04,0:08:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...because they said they'd rescue me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.59,0:08:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one will come, you dumb woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.22,0:08:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone will burn to death in\Nthe raging fire of Buster Call!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.18,0:08:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll even erase the utter humiliation of the fact\Nthat pirates shot through our sacred flag!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.74,0:09:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like in Ohara twenty years ago,\Nwhen that giant marine attacked us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.83,0:09:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.07,0:09:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Walk with your own two feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.02,0:09:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saul...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.36,0:09:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.60,0:09:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief! Please hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.63,0:09:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! Shut up! I'm a hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.63,0:09:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably think that I don't\Nknow anything about it, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.60,0:09:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The misconduct by Jaguar D. Saul,\Na former Navy Headquarters Vice Admiral!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.18,0:09:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mother, Olvia...\NWhat happened in Ohara at that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.58,0:09:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know about it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.96,0:09:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because I was told.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.63,0:09:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who commanded a raid on\Nthe land of Ohara, where devils lived,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.95,0:09:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,exposed their terrible crime\Nand issued a Buster Call
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.95,0:09:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was my old man, then-CP9 Chief Spandine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.18,0:10:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, scholars of Ohara!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.98,0:10:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your death sentence has now been decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.80,0:10:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminate him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.52,0:10:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.00,0:10:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ohara has...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.75,0:10:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...come to know too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.26,0:10:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll initiate a Buster Call!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.58,0:10:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, go, Saul!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.72,0:10:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.86,0:10:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I'll stay here, too! Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.41,0:11:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.08,0:11:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was happy to hear you call me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.61,0:11:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.70,0:11:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, for you and me both...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.54,0:11:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Live, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.40,0:11:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They all thought that everyone\Nin Ohara at that time died, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.96,0:11:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Government missed\None brat who escaped then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.31,0:11:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.82,0:11:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows how many times this\Neight-year-old brat almost got killed
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.01,0:11:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by adults who wanted money...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.10,0:11:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't trust anyone who came near you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.19,0:11:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You had nowhere you could sleep safe\Nand sound. You didn't have food, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.09,0:11:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even wanna imagine how crappy\Nthe last twenty years were for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.25,0:11:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were so unhappy it'd make you cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.21,0:12:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The person who put a bounty\Non your head twenty years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was my old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.68,0:12:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did it for world peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.34,0:12:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, after twenty years...\Nhis son hunts down the only survivor,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.52,0:12:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the battle of Ohara comes to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.68,0:12:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ohara lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.59,0:12:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin! Be proud, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.08,0:12:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mom is honorable! Ohara is honorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.74,0:12:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, pass down this\Nisland's history, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.43,0:12:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ohara fought against the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.65,0:12:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not while I'm still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.76,0:13:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're gonna die, aren't you?! Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.07,0:13:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.95,0:13:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Cutty Flam! What is he doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.92,0:13:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's okay. He fell for it! How stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.78,0:13:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot got caught in the landmine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.22,0:13:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He came to rescue me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.13,0:13:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops. This isn't good. It was\Ngood that I made doubly sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.06,0:13:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've gotta hurry. Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.47,0:13:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even put it in words...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.73,0:13:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Set sail, marines! I'm gonna jump on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.35,0:13:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir! Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.40,0:13:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're setting sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.82,0:13:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.39,0:13:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so angry that I can't stop my tears!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.03,0:13:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just watch carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.54,0:14:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first step of a hero\Nthat will be engraved in histo...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.83,0:14:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just watch carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.34,0:14:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first step of a hero\Nthat will be engraved in histo...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.37,0:14:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha-cha houie ouchie owow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.47,0:14:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Chief?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.12,0:14:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?! Who did this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.96,0:14:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one on the bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.48,0:14:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There must be! They must be\Nhiding somewhere! Find them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.79,0:15:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.13,0:15:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What're you guys doing?!\NWhy aren't you attacking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.37,0:15:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Chief, we can't find the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.55,0:15:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.13,0:15:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run with all your might!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.21,0:15:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll die if you stay on the island!\NSail out on my raft!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.92,0:15:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Saul?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.25,0:15:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it for me. I got caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.90,0:15:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Go!\N--No! There's no one on the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.23,0:15:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.44,0:15:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're alone now, but you'll\Nmeet friends someday for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.32,0:16:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. The sea is vast, so someday, definitely...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.12,0:16:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'll come across friends who'll protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.42,0:16:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one is born into this world to be alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.33,0:16:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, Robin! Don't look back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.30,0:16:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're having a hard time,\Nlaugh like this, just like I taught you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.16,0:16:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out, Saul!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.86,0:16:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.36,0:16:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saul!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.16,0:16:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go meet the friends\Nwho're surely waiting for you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,somewhere at sea, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.84,0:16:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Live together with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.01,0:17:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief! Please look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.34,0:17:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! What?! Where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.20,0:17:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.35,0:17:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of the Tower of Law...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.19,0:17:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tower of Law?! What can\Nhe do from that far away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.28,0:17:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Snap!\N--Who the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.70,0:17:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--♪ I was born... ♪\N--He's aiming at us from that distance\Nwithout the slightest error, in this wind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.50,0:17:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--♪ ...on the island of snipers ♪\N--Who the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.02,0:17:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long-nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.95,0:17:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See that?! Our sniper is amazing, isn't he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.16,0:17:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--♪ Or even your heart... ♪\N--Damn well serves them right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.72,0:17:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-chan! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.75,0:17:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ ...lock on!! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.53,0:17:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does he really have to sing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.31,0:17:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.53,0:18:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.03,0:18:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! What're you guys doing?!\NShoot him dead already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.80,0:18:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're trying, but our bullets won't\Nreach that far, much less hit him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.70,0:18:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sniper's got really incredible skills!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.54,0:18:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nico Robin is getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.42,0:18:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let her get away!\NIdiots! You can shoot her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.28,0:18:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yes, sir!\N--Shoot her dead enough to keep her alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.47,0:18:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.15,0:18:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.37,0:18:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.66,0:19:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.49,0:19:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.33,0:19:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My body is strong because it's iron.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.42,0:19:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That landmine wasn't nice, Spanda!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.11,0:19:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eek!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.73,0:19:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... Franky-kun, Franky-kun.\NThis is Sogeking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.58,0:19:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Oh? This transponder\Nsnail is supposed to...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.55,0:19:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it from Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.81,0:19:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, you should find a\Nred cloth bundle on the ground near you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.91,0:19:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Red cloth?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.38,0:19:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.06,0:19:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got two keys in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.97,0:19:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Together with your keys,\Nyou should have all the keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.82,0:19:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the keys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.41,0:19:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I delivered them to you without fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.50,0:19:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mission accomplished.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.78,0:20:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry. This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.40,0:20:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#1...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.66,0:20:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#3...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.11,0:20:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#4... Doesn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.74,0:20:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#5!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.68,0:20:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They came off!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.82,0:20:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not possible! Th-They're the real keys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.66,0:20:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey... Pull yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.71,0:20:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no... Does this mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.10,0:20:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh! You guys defeated everyone\Nin CP9 in the Tower of Law?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.98,0:20:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that can't be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.79,0:20:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must've stolen them and run! Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.18,0:20:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Franky! Hey, Long-nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.65,0:20:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got the handcuffs off of Nico Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.03,0:20:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.91,0:20:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Long-nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.58,0:21:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can thank those who fought hard\Nto gather the keys when this is all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.59,0:21:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are, without a doubt,\None of Luffy-kun's gang!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.77,0:21:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can now do as you wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.89,0:21:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.55,0:21:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seis... Fleurs!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.35,0:21:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.18,0:21:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Slap!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.71,0:21:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.54,0:21:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do this to my heart's content.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.75,0:21:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.36,0:21:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, guys! Hurry up and get over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.76,0:21:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get things ready for our escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.22,0:21:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.89,0:21:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come down already, Sogeking!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.31,0:22:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad! The Sea Prism Stone\Nhandcuffs are off of the criminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.86,0:22:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Capture her again!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.18,0:22:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything went according to my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.68,0:22:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.72,0:22:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I hear something just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.24,0:22:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if my body falls apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.50,0:22:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do whatever I can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.72,0:22:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not really smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.66,0:22:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That technique of yours is\Nshortening your life, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.81,0:22:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too ambitious!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.27,0:22:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.48,0:22:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Robin Freed! Luffy vs. Lucci,\NShowdown Between Leaders"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.48,0:22:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
